title: It Never Ends
description: The exploits of Doctor Tad Winslow. Like the cleaning of a house… it never ends.
quote: This relationship can never work. I’m a doctor and you’re a 5,000 year old mummy I brought back to life.
altHero: portrait drawings of characters from the show: a nun, a woman in a tiara, and a man with an eye patch
alt1: Doctor Tad Winslow in a hot tub with Gabriela Sinparch
alt2: Tad opens the door and it‘s Homer Simpson dressed as an angel
alt3: Tad with angel Homer who’s holding an “It Never Ends” book
alt4: angel Homer reads from the book
